snippet.title: Lucent Memories - Terraria: The Stars Above 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
The next step in the journey is on the horizon...
https://discord.gg/starsabove | Join the Discord today!

With new abilities, a new weapon upgrade system, new weapons, new Cosmic Voyages, new bosses, boss reworks, new original songs, and so much more, The Stars Above again is rejuvenated with tons of content to explore. The adventure continues!

Featuring one of the new Stars Above original tracks, "Legends Yet Unspun" composed by ShadyCicada!
